            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-f91b7ebecc26747b-4e8794 twpub-f91b7ebecc26747b-37337d twpub-f91b7ebecc26747b-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"boxxx\"><div class=\"blockquot2\"><p>More stories of the sort you like; more, probably, by the author of this one; more than 500 titles all told by writers of world-wide reputation, in the Authors’ Alphabetical List which you will find on the <i>reverse side</i> of the wrapper of this book. Look it over before you lay it aside. There are books here you are sure to want—some, possibly, that you have <i>always</i> wanted.</p></div></div></div>"
        },
